routeFacts.name: S-Bahn Zentralschweiz
routeFacts.description: S-Bahn Zentralschweiz is a route for Train Sim World 2 developed by Rivet Games. Set in Switzerland, it features the Luzern S-Bahn line between Luzern and Sursee, featuring local S1 services as well as express RE trains. Both types of services use the SBB RABe 523. This route features the first implementation of ETCS (Level 1) in Train Sim World 2 at speeds of up to 160km/h.
routeInfo: S-Bahn Zentralschweiz covers the 26 kilometre route from Luzern to Sursee in central Switzerland, focusing on commuter services.
